      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some fading in the clear coat and a handful of small dings and surface scratches. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear and some minor staining. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may soon require some routine maintenance like new brakes or tires to keep it in top shape.",
