    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car runs like a dream and is incredibly comfy. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love, as any reliable car does, but it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
