      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 hp with a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to a finely tuned suspension geometry designed for maximum mechanical grip and telegraphic feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing critical structural areas for this platform. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are strong, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that modern cars fail to replicate.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
