    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with every button and dial functioning exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is in excellent health, having been serviced regularly with synthetic oil and high-quality filters. It shifts smoothly, accelerates with confidence, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the air conditioning blows ice-cold even in peak summer heat. This is a well-cared-for example that is ready for its next chapter and many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
